{"readme":"<h1 class=\"title\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://github.com/Jam3/css-transform-to-mat4\">css-transform-to-mat4</a><div class=\"contrib\"></div></h1>\n<p><a href=\"http://github.com/badges/stability-badges\"></a></p>\n<p>Will take a string which is a css transform value (2d or 3d) and return a mat4 or 3d transformation matrix from the string.</p>\n<h2 id=\"usage\">Usage</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.npmjs.com/package/css-transform-to-mat4\"></a></p>\n<h3 id=\"example-\">Example:</h3>\n<pre><code class=\"lang-javascript\"><div class=\"line\"><span class=\"source js\"><span class=\"storage modifier js\"><span>var</span></span><span>&#xA0;getMatrix&#xA0;</span><span class=\"keyword operator js\"><span>=</span></span><span>&#xA0;</span><span class=\"support function js\"><span>require</span></span><span class=\"meta brace round js\"><span>(</span></span><span class=\"string quoted single js\"><span class=\"punctuation definition string begin js\"><span>&apos;</span></span><span>css-transform-to-mat4</span><span class=\"punctuation definition string end js\"><span>&apos;</span></span></span><span class=\"meta brace round js\"><span>)</span></span><span class=\"punctuation terminator statement js\"><span>;</span></span></span></div><div class=\"line\"><span class=\"source js\"><span>&#xA0;</span></span></div><div class=\"line\"><span class=\"source js\"><span class=\"storage modifier js\"><span>var</span></span><span>&#xA0;matrix3DA&#xA0;</span><span class=\"keyword operator js\"><span>=</span></span><span>&#xA0;getMatrix</span><span class=\"meta brace round js\"><span>(</span></span><span class=\"string quoted single js\"><span class=\"punctuation definition string begin js\"><span>&apos;</span></span><span>translate(40px,&#xA0;20px)</span><span class=\"punctuation definition string end js\"><span>&apos;</span></span></span><span class=\"meta brace round js\"><span>)</span></span><span class=\"punctuation terminator statement js\"><span>;</span></span><span>&#xA0;</span><span class=\"comment line double-slash js\"><span class=\"punctuation definition comment js\"><span>//</span></span><span>&#xA0;works&#xA0;with&#xA0;2d&#xA0;transforms</span><span>&#xA0;</span></span></span></div><div class=\"line\"><span class=\"source js\"><span class=\"storage modifier js\"><span>var</span></span><span>&#xA0;matrix3DB&#xA0;</span><span class=\"keyword operator js\"><span>=</span></span><span>&#xA0;getMatrix</span><span class=\"meta brace round js\"><span>(</span></span><span class=\"string quoted single js\"><span class=\"punctuation definition string begin js\"><span>&apos;</span></span><span>perspective(1000px)&#xA0;translate3d(40px,&#xA0;20px,&#xA0;-1000px)</span><span class=\"punctuation definition string end js\"><span>&apos;</span></span></span><span class=\"meta brace round js\"><span>)</span></span><span class=\"punctuation terminator statement js\"><span>;</span></span><span>&#xA0;</span><span class=\"comment line double-slash js\"><span class=\"punctuation definition comment js\"><span>//</span></span><span>&#xA0;and&#xA0;3d</span><span>&#xA0;</span></span></span></div>\n</code></pre>\n<p>To see more examples check out:\n<a href=\"http://requirebin.com/?gist=adf102de923cf6f1dc82\">http://requirebin.com/?gist=adf102de923cf6f1dc82</a></p>\n<h2 id=\"license\">License</h2>\n<p>MIT, see <a href=\"http://github.com/Jam3/css-transform-to-mat4/blob/master/LICENSE.md\">LICENSE.md</a> for details.</p>\n"}